<p><u>Senator Cranston’s Chief Fundraiser</u></p>

<p>In 1984, Jacobson began working for <a href="/actors/senators/Alan-Cranston">
Senator Cranston</a> as a Senate staff member. In 1987, she shifted roles and
became his “Fundraising Coordinator.” Jacobson was present at a number of the meetings
attended by Cranston, <a href="/actors/affiliates/James-Grogan">James Grogan</a>,
and <a href="/actors/affiliates/Charles-Keating">Charles Keating</a>.</p>

